47
00:04:03,506 --> 00:04:05,006
Apa itu benar?

48
00:04:06,206 --> 00:04:07,706
Kau tikus kurang ajar!

49
00:04:12,906 --> 00:04:15,606
Siapa yang di telepon tadi?

50
00:04:15,606 --> 00:04:18,406
Seorang pria memintaku menyelidiki perselingkuhan istrinya, jadi kulakukan.

51
00:04:18,406 --> 00:04:20,806
