Kau...

81
00:06:16,506 --> 00:06:18,606
Eisuke Hondou.

82
00:06:18,606 --> 00:06:20,606
Halo.

83
00:06:20,606 --> 00:06:22,306
Oh, tidak! Maafkan aku!

84
