00:06:40,306 --> 00:06:42,306
Kurasa begitu.

91
00:06:42,306 --> 00:06:43,906
Biarkan aku membantumu!

92
00:06:43,906 --> 00:06:45,406
Aku akan terima teleponmu atau melakukan apa saja!

93
00:06:49,306 --> 00:06:52,806
Ya, ini Agensi Detektif Mouri.

94
00:06:52,806 --> 00:06:55,506
Halo? Halo?

95
00:06:56,806 --> 00:06:57,906
Hei.

96
00:07:01,406 --> 00:07:03,506
Hah? Itu aneh.

97
00:07:03,506 --> 00:07:04,506
Mereka menutupnya.

98
00:07:05,806 --> 00:07:08,806
Maksudku, kau yang melakukannya dan menutupnya sendiri!

99
00:07:14,606 --> 00:07:16,806
Dengar, jangan sentuh apapun!

100
00:07:16,806 --> 00:07:18,106
Ya, pak.

