165
00:10:26,906 --> 00:10:29,906
Aku berusaha meneleponmu sebelum datang ke sini,

166
00:10:29,906 --> 00:10:33,306
tapi untuk beberapa alasan, sambungannya terputus.

167
00:10:34,306 --> 00:10:35,306
Oh, tidak.

168
00:10:37,106 --> 00:10:38,306
Hei.

169
00:10:38,306 --> 00:10:42,306
Takumi, kau tahu di jembatan mana kau melihatnya?

170
00:10:42,306 --> 00:10:43,906
Aku melihatnya kemarin lusa.

171
00:10:43,906 --> 00:10:46,206
Tapi aku tidak tahu di mana.

172
00:10:47,906 --> 00:10:49,806
Aku dengar suara kembang api.

173
00:10:49,806 --> 00:10:51,006
Jika kemarin lusa,

174
00:10:51,006 --> 00:10:53,706
